title: Indigo® A3 White Multipurpose Copier Paper – 80gsm, Ideal for Printing, Copying & Office Use (100 Sheets)
features: High-Quality 80gsm Weight – Provides a perfect balance of durability and smoothness for professional-grade prints.
A3 Size (420 x 297mm) – Ideal for large documents, reports, presentations, and creative projects.
Compatible with Laser & Inkjet Printers – Works seamlessly with a wide range of devices, including copiers and standard fax machines.
Exceptional Print Quality – Offers sharp text, vibrant colours, and excellent contrast for both black-and-white and colour prints.
Versatile Use – Perfect for office documents, reports, memos, meeting notes, and creative hobbies such as art and crafts.
Reliable and Smooth Performance – Ensures consistent, jam-free operation across printers, copiers, and fax machines.
Available in 50 or 100 Sheet Packs – Convenient pack sizes for small and large printing jobs.
Professional Finish – Provides crisp, clear images and text, enhancing the readability and appearance of your documents.
Perfect for Spot Colour Printing – Suitable for both mono and colour printing, ensuring versatility in your projects.
description: Product Description Office Efficiency Office Efficiency Elevate your business communications with our premium multipurpose copier papers. Discover the perfect paper companion to fuel your productivity and unlock your potential. Experience the clarity, precision, and professional finish that our papers deliver. Whether you're printing important business reports or eye-catching marketing materials, our papers consistently deliver exceptional results. Uncompromising Quality for Exceptional Results Our premium multipurpose copier papers are designed to meet the highest standards of quality and performance. With exceptional whiteness, smooth finish, and excellent printability, our papers ensure that your documents, presentations, and creative projects stand out with precision and clarity. Discover a World of Variety At Indigo, we believe in offering a diverse range of options to cater to your specific needs. We understand that every project and printing requirement is unique, which is why we offer a wide variety of our premium multipurpose copier papers. Our collection includes an array of sizes and weights, ensuring that you find the perfect fit for your printing endeavors. From the lightweight and versatile 80gsm paper to the sturdy and durable 90gsm options, you can select the ideal thickness that aligns with your printing requirements. We even have the premium 160gsm cardstock for those special projects that demand extra durability and a touch of elegance. But it doesn't stop there. Our multipurpose copier papers are available in both 50-sheet and 100-sheet packs, allowing you to choose the quantity that best suits your needs.
